lead_paragraph: Giovani dos Santos scored to help the Los Angeles Galaxy tie Sporting Kansas City 1-1 and extend its unbeaten streak to six games Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Dos Santos Stays Hot as Galaxy Plays Sporting KC to 1-1 Draw
